Detailed Description

Lookup table for modulation level adjustment. This table consists of x and y values as separate arrays. So x[i], y[i] define the (x,y) coordinates of point i of the lookup table.

Note:
The x values must be monotonically increasing to produce correct results during linear interpolation.
